ons are fullfilled : $\\alpha_1$\nparameter positive and the Higgs mass hierarchy\n$m_{h_{3}}>m_{H_2^\\pm}>m_{H^{\\pm\\pm}}$.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 May 2023 00:15:50 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-16"}
