ws an extended form\nkeeping the redshift information as an independent coordinate and can also be\nreadily degraded to the form of a traditional combined method to constrain\nparameters.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 May 2023 02:27:25 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-16"}
