uclear and interstellar media of\nhost galaxies. It can only be slightly alleviated by the standard hard X-ray\nand far-UV extinction cuts used by Lusso et al. (2020). Consequently, the\n$L_{X}-L_{UV}$ relation QSO data compilation of Lusso et al. (2020) cannot be\nused for cosmological purposes.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Sun, 14 May 2023 15:05:21 GMT"}],"update_date":"2023-05-16"}
